<h1 class="how_to_use">How to use</h1>
<h3>
  When refering to topup.holder.nl (the easiest setup)
</h3>
<ol>
  <li>
    Include TopUp with the following:
    <span class="code">
      &lt;script type="text/javascript" src="http://topup.holder.nl/releases/latest/top_up.js"></script>
    </span>
    (for a specific version use /releases/1.3.2/top_up.js for example)
  </li>
  <li>
    Enjoy!
  </li>
</ol>
<h3>
  When hosting the source and images yourself
</h3>
<ol>
  <li>
    Download the <%= link_to "latest TopUp version", "http://topup.holder.nl/releases/packed/latest" %>
  </li>
  <li>
    Include TopUp with the following:
    <span class="code">
      &lt;script type="text/javascript" src="path/to/your/top_up.js"></script>
    </span>
  </li>
  <li>
    Enjoy!
  </li>
</ol>
<p>
  For further documentation go to the <%= link_to "documentation page", "/documentation" %>
</p>

